# RAGAS evaluation fixtures
#
# FR-KG-04 Phase 10 Task 10.2 (openspec change
# fix-fr-kg-04-schema-drift-and-sync-hardening).
#
# Add fixture JSON files here following the format documented in
# docs/ragas-evaluation.md. Example filename: linear-algebra.json.
#
# Each file must contain:
#   - "topic": string identifier for this topic area
#   - "cases": list of {query, expected_retrieval_contexts, ground_truth_answer}
#
# The .gitkeep placeholder ensures this directory exists in git history
# even before the first real fixture is added. Remove it once the first
# fixture is committed.
